Layout/EmptyLinesAroundAccessModifier.description:
Description

Keep blank lines around access modifiers.
Layout/EmptyLinesAroundAccessModifier.option:
This rule supports the following parameters in your configuration:

EnforcedStyle: around (type: str)
SupportedStyles: ['around', 'only_before'] (type: list)
References: ['https://edgeguides.rubyonrails.org/contributing_to_ruby_on_rails.html#follow-the-coding-conventions'] (type: list)
